        <prompt>How did the development of the Pullman Palace Car Company impact railroad travel?</prompt>
        <options>
            <option letter="a">It revolutionized passenger comfort and created a system of luxury rail travel</option>
            <option letter="b">It focused only on freight transportation</option>
            <option letter="c">It made rail travel more affordable</option>
            <option letter="d">It operated only in the Northeast</option>
        </options>
        <answer>a</answer>
        <explanation>George Pullman's company transformed rail travel by introducing luxury sleeping cars and dining cars, while also creating a significant workforce of African American porters.</explanation>
